      <title>特朗普重返 OPEC 政坛使下个月的石油谈判变得复杂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-s-return-to-opec-politics-complicates-oil-talks-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普呼吁 OPEC+ 降低油价，此举加大了下个月 OPEC 部长级会议的赌注。]]></description>
